          "body": {
            "text": "Formerly known as Lyse Kyrka, after the beautiful church nearby. A popular crag for courses, and it is easy to see why: fine, long, easy routes, easy top-roping from the large ledge above, a shelter for lunch, and only a short walk from the car.\n\nFormerly known as Lyse Kyrka, after the beautiful church near the crag. This crag has relatively easy routes, good top-rope options and easy access, just a short walk from the car.",
